+# PW-D01: Playwright Runner And Project Bootstrap Contract
+
+## Status
+
+**Proposed.** This decision becomes accepted only after independent review of
+the exact pull-request head SHA and merge by Eddie or the Operator.
+
+## Governance And Scope
+
+| Field | Value |
+|---|---|
+| Work item | `slarti/backlog#254` (`PW-D01`) |
+| Frozen plan | `playwright-execution-plan-v1` |
+| Frozen plan approval | `yeraziael/slartis-backlog#83`, review `4757129666` |
+| Approved plan head | `d1379fbb065b0888e1615bce49205384b3f1a4ba` |
+| Architecture base | `ed54f1144f1df21af13c9a2a1fd5c685fa2a95ac` |
+| Execution mode | Sol high, architecture decision only |
+
+This document selects the immutable runner and Node project contract consumed
+by PW-I01. It does not create the project, install dependencies, edit CI, pull
+the image into a production runtime, execute a browser, or change any service.
+
+## Context
+
+The shared browser platform requires one local/CI execution contract with no
+host Node.js dependency, no persistent browser service, no mutable image tag,
+and no package-manager choice left to a low-cost implementation agent.
+
+The official Playwright image contains browser binaries and system libraries,
+but not the `@playwright/test` project dependency. The image version and project
+package version must match exactly or Playwright may not find the bundled
+browsers.
+
+The Gitea Actions runner and the Architecture workstation are linux/amd64. The
+Pi5 is not a browser runner and is outside this decision.
+
+## Decision Summary
+
+| Concern | Decision |
+|---|---|
+| Playwright release | `1.61.1` |
+| Image tag | `mcr.microsoft.com/playwright:v1.61.1-noble` |
+| Multi-platform index digest | `sha256:5b8f294aff9041b7191c34a4bab3ac270157a28774d4b0660e9743297b697e48` |
+| Selected linux/amd64 manifest | `sha256:cf0daee9b994042e011bc29f20cdff1a9f682a039b43fcd738f7d8a9d3bcd9d6` |
+| Runtime image reference | `mcr.microsoft.com/playwright:v1.61.1-noble@sha256:cf0daee9b994042e011bc29f20cdff1a9f682a039b43fcd738f7d8a9d3bcd9d6` |
+| Base OS | Ubuntu 24.04 LTS (Noble) |
+| Platform | `linux/amd64` |
+| Node.js | `24.17.0`, supplied by the pinned image |
+| npm | `11.13.0`, supplied by the pinned image |
+| Test package | `@playwright/test@1.61.1` exactly |
+| Required browser project | Chromium only |
+| Chromium binary | Chrome for Testing `149.0.7827.55`, revision `1228` |
+| Package manager | npm; no pnpm, Yarn, or host package manager |
+| Lock file | committed `tests/playwright/package-lock.json`, lockfile version 3 |
+| Project module mode | ECMAScript modules (`"type": "module"`) |
+| Package script | `playwright test --config=playwright.config.ts --project=chromium` |
